content: I am a Ph.D. student at the Computer Science Department of Tsinghua University, under the supervision of Prof. Lifeng Sun and Prof. Zhi Wang. Prior to joining the Lab of Multimedia and Networking, I received my B.S. degree from School of Computer Science and Technology at Sun Yat-Sen University. My research work focuses on the multimedia network optimization. For more details, please refer to my CV.
